        body: `The data, estimates, metrics, and analyses in this report are generated through artificial intelligence and large language models (LLMs). ${brandName} makes no warranties regarding accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of the data. This report is provided "AS IS" for informational and strategic diagnostic purposes only. Traffic figures, DA, backlinks, and ranking data are predictive estimates and should not be used as certified metrics or financial statements.`,
