        body: `This document is for the exclusive use of the client or user who generated it within the Platform. It is expressly PROHIBITED to: (a) commercialize, sell, or license this report to third parties without ${brandName}'s written authorization; (b) present the data as your own without attributing ${brandName} as the source; (c) use the results for direct competition against ${brandName} or its products. Violations may result in civil and criminal legal action.`,
